OL,5, Four staff at a special needs school   
OL,6, have "lost their jobs" after an audio  
OL,7, recording revealed concerns around     
OL,8, staff conduct towards children.        
OL,10,FAs reported by the Essex Daily Gazette,
OL,11,Fan accidental recording on a pupil's   
OL,12,FiPad captured a full day within a      
OL,13,Fclassroom at Market Field School.      
OL,15,FThe child's mother found the file and  
OL,16,Fnotified the school about the content. 
OL,18,FHeadteacher Ruth Whitehead said she    
OL,19,Fconcluded "gross misconduct" occurred  
OL,20,Fand apologised to parents in a letter. 
